{"tid":401713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩：近乎完成核計劃　終極目標與美國實力平衡","createTime":"2017-09-15T23:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T00:10:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97a22face70cf93da186580df1da1b7c4df17796","tid":401713,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T23:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/075308_75b33418a4bdf4c5e6a40f197eee5d54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F075308_75b33418a4bdf4c5e6a40f197eee5d54.jpg&h=6c5b5bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方朝鮮中央通訊社稱，朝鮮勞動黨委員長、國務委員會委員長、人民軍最高司令官金正恩昨天親自臨場指導「火星－12」中遠程戰略彈道導彈發射訓練，聲稱朝鮮最終目標是與美國保持實力平衡，而朝鮮在達到國家核力量完善目標上「已幾乎達到終點」。<br />\n<br />\n朝中社稱，昨天的導彈發射訓練目的，是進一步加強壓制美國近期大談對朝鮮使用軍事力量的好戰性，並以迅速而強有力軍事反制措施予以回應、檢驗核彈頭使用秩序、確認實戰行動程序。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩指這次導彈發射訓練在核力量戰力化中具有重大意義並達到預期目的，他表示極大滿意。他又說，朝鮮最終目標是與美國保持實際性實力平衡，保證美國當政者的嘴裏不再恣意拋出對朝鮮軍事選擇等胡言亂語；朝鮮要繼續從質量上鞏固軍事攻擊能力，給予美國無法承受的核反擊，繼續徑直向前奔馳。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩表示，朝鮮是在數十年持續不斷的聯合國制裁中擁有了現在的一切，而非在聯合國的任何「施惠」中得來的。他譏諷以大國自居的部分國家還在執迷於聯合國制裁、指望屈服朝鮮，「真偏執透頂了」。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩強調，要讓大國主義者清楚地看到朝鮮在其無止境的制裁和封鎖中如何達到國家核力量完善目標，且現在已幾乎達到終點。<br />\n<br />\n另外，路透社引述中國駐美大使崔天凱表示，中國永遠不會接受朝鮮成為核武國家，他同時要求美國克制，勿恫嚇朝鮮，並應多致力恢復對話和談判。"},{"pid":"e0fbb8cf10adcd58cc3d25b9f9951350193f02d3","tid":401713,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T23:53:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170916/s00005/1505518938603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170916%2Fs00005%2F1505518938603&d=PwBGKwisCUV%2FBu%2FFbY7d754%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2a33f0d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170916%2Fs00005%2F1505518938603&h=15cf0613\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170916/s00005/1505518938603</a>"},{"pid":"b900408949ecb2036ef1558abc401f8d71376edd","tid":401713,"uid":76470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T23:55:03.000Z","msg":"隔離個個金仔老婆？"},{"pid":"2e1d43ccdc7c3211e3aed03f18fe9a1d5a756750","tid":401713,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43c1fe7aeb929c63d7b64e1f93dedf202a5d6787","tid":401713,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:23:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李雪主 正撚到</blockquote><br />\n諗起金仔瘋狂un李雪主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d300b7af685530c23cbf3c5b93b3781beb3c47c7","tid":401713,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:26:53.000Z","msg":"同其他國家元首玩換妻計畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9458a77652f5eeb9a9fac85b36fac2127351d63","tid":401713,"uid":62121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:57:25.000Z","msg":"又一個Dior 李雪主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1aec64e476e12583a34b4463b7ffb18cac17b45","tid":401713,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同其他國家元首玩換妻計畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n金仔可以屌鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同trump 換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a543c70f40048fdc76bd15bfd1d8a1db471862f","tid":401713,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:31:23.000Z","msg":"條女漲卜卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"